short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Easily bookmark and access Automateo workflow apps

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Automateo Workflow Bookmarker is a simple Chrome extension that helps you easily bookmark and access your favorite Automateo workflow apps. With just a few clicks, you can save and organize workflows, making it quick and efficient to revisit and execute them whenever needed.

Whether you're managing multiple workflows or simply want fast access to frequently used tools, this extension streamlines the process, ensuring you stay productive. If you're an Automateo user, this extension is a must-have for seamless workflow management.
